OL,3,CStrictly Come Dancing's Karen Hauer
OL,4,Cquits show after 14 years
OL,6,FStrictly Come Dancing professional
OL,7,Fdancer Karen Hauer has quit the show
OL,8,Fafter 14 years.
OL,10,FShe announced her decision on
OL,11,FSaturday, saying was "the right time
OL,12,Fto close this chapter and take on new
OL,13,Fprojects in other areas I'm passionate
OL,14,Fabout".
OL,16,FThe Venezuela-born dancer addressed
OL,17,Fformer co-hosts Claudia Winkleman and
OL,18,FTess Daly, who stepped down last year,
OL,19,Fsaying "maybe now we can finally be
OL,20,Fladies who lunch in the Autumn".
OL,26,@sD@VOUvD@FO]{D@HOU|D@_O]
