OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774260876
OL,3,CStrictly Come Dancing's Karen Hauer
OL,4,Cquits show after 14 years
OL,6,FIn a video shared to her Instagram
OL,7,Faccount, she told her followers:
OL,8,F"Strictly completely changed my life,
OL,9,Fnot only as a performer and a teacher
OL,10,Fbut as a human being.
OL,12,F"I've had the privilege of meeting so
OL,13,Fmany incredible people and brilliant
OL,14,Fcelebrity partners who have become
OL,15,Fclose friends and people I admire so
OL,16,Fmuch."
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
