OL,3,CStrictly Come Dancing's Karen Hauer
OL,4,Cquits show after 14 years
OL,6,FHauer thanked her fans who have
OL,7,F"witnessed all of my different
OL,8,Fhairstyles" and the Strictly crew
OL,9,Fincluding the welfare team who "take
OL,10,Fsuch good care of us".
OL,12,F"I'll never forget joining the show 14
OL,13,Fyears ago with Sir Bruce Forsyth and
OL,14,FLen Goodman and learning from such
OL,15,Fincredible legends along the way."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@KO]qD@`OUrD@UO]tD@AOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
