PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774260876
OL,3,CStrictly Come Dancing's Karen Hauer
OL,4,Cquits show after 14 years
OL,6,FShe added: "I'll even miss standing
OL,7,Ffront of the judges, can you believe
OL,8,Fthat? Smiling politely while sometimes
OL,9,Fsecretly disagreeing ` it's been an
OL,10,Fhonour to share the ballroom with
OL,11,Fthem."
OL,13,FThe award-winning dancer became
OL,14,Femotional as she said: "Who would've
OL,15,Fthought that a young girl from the
OL,16,FBronx would end up becoming the
OL,17,Flongest serving female professional
OL,18,Fdancer on a British TV institution."
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@FO]vD@XOUzD@dO]
