PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774260876
OL,3,CStrictly Come Dancing's Karen Hauer
OL,4,Cquits show after 14 years
OL,6,FSarah James, executive producer at
OL,7,FStrictly, said in a statement: "As the
OL,8,Flongest-serving female professional
OL,9,Fdancer in the history of the show,
OL,10,FKaren has given so much of herself and
OL,11,Fher time to the programme, and we are
OL,12,Fextremely grateful for the passion,
OL,13,Fcreativity and dedication she has
OL,14,Fbrought to every single performance.
OL,16,F"She has captivated audiences with her
OL,17,Ftalent, warmth and genuine love of
OL,18,Fdance and has been responsible for
OL,19,Fsome of the most iconic partnerships
OL,20,Fand joyous routines the Strictly dance
OL,21,Ffloor has ever seen.
OL,26,@oD@`OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
