PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774260876
OL,3,CStrictly Come Dancing's Karen Hauer
OL,4,Cquits show after 14 years
OL,6,F"We thank her for all these memorable
OL,7,Fmoments and for her incredible work
OL,8,Fethic.
OL,10,F"Her professionalism and sense of
OL,11,Fhumour shine through everything she
OL,12,Fachieves and we can't wait to see
OL,13,Fwhere her next chapter takes her."
OL,15,FHauer's departure comes amid reports
OL,16,Fthat several professional dancers on
OL,17,Fthe show have been axed ahead of the
OL,18,Fupcoming series.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@bO]
